item.title: Whats a good base server for a newb coder?
item.dc:creator: @NewbieNewty Newty
item.description:
@NewbieNewty wrote:

Delta or Czar will be the easiest for you too start coding on, although, people will flame you for using those bases.

But yeah, for a beginner, I recommend Delta.
